Author: shittypebbles
Text: Idk about movies, but Megan Draper from Mad Men definitely displays many signs of an eating disorder. She uses food as comfort for everyone else and is first to offer to make something. But we never see her eat anything except at that diner in defiance of Don.  I'm really sad they didn't go more into it explicitly.
